title: The Attache - 1 Bedroom $735 - Pet Friendly
posting_body: ['The Attache Apartments located at 17525 Madison Avenue are minutes from bars, restaurants, downtown Lakewood, and Rocky River.', '1 Bedroom', 'https://youtu.be/jjDT0t--h0A', '* Photos/videos may be of other units in the building, not the available unit.', 'Features', 'Tenant responsible for electricity', 'Landlord pays for gas, water, sewer, trash, and heat', 'Laundry in building', 'Secure Entry', 'Lot (first come) parking included', 'Pet Policy: This location accepts cats, limit 2 pets per unit.', '$25/pet/month, no pet deposit.', 'Application Process', 'The non refundable application fee is $35 for the first application and $5 for any additional applications, anyone 18 or over who intends to reside in the apartment must submit an application.', 'We accept cash, check, money order, and debit card.', "Applications must be filled out in their entirety and submitted with photo ID and proof of income (last 4 weeks/last 2-4 pay stubs from current job, or if self employed last 3 months of bank statements showing deposits, or if receiving social security this year's letter).", 'Please call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a tour or for an application.', 'We have several properties in the neighborhood, at AIY Properties we are confident that we have an apartment that fits your budget and preferences.', 'Please contact us at', 'show contact info', 'or <URL>.']
